3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Patricia Helen Heaton (4 de marzo de 1958) es una actriz estadounidense ganadora de un premio Emmy, conocida principalmente por su interpretación de Debra Barone, la esposa de Ray Barone, en la comedia de situaciones Everybody Loves Raymond. Entre septiembre de 2007 y mayo de 2008 regresó a la televisión junto a Kelsey Grammer en la serie cómica Back To You de la cadena FOX. Actualmente es protagonista de la comedia The Middle, junto a Neil Flynn y Chris Kattan.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Patricia Helen Heaton (* 4. März 1958 in Bay Village, Ohio) ist eine US-amerikanische Schauspielerin.\n\nIhre bisher bedeutsamste Rolle war die der Debra Barone in der US-Sitcom Alle lieben Raymond an der Seite von Ray Romano. Für ihre Darstellung war Heaton sieben Mal als beste Hauptdarstellerin in einer Comedy-Serie für einen Emmy-Award nominiert. 2000 und 2001 gewann Heaton den Preis. Von 2009 bis 2018 spielte sie in der Serie The Middle die Hauptfigur Frankie Heck.\n\nAm 22. Mai 2012 wurde Heaton mit einem Stern auf dem Hollywood Walk of Fame ausgezeichnet.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"帕特里夏·海伦·希顿（Patricia Helen Heaton，1958年3月4日-），美国女演员。她因在 CBS 情景喜剧《人人都爱雷蒙德》（1996-2005 年）中饰演黛布拉·巴隆 （Debra Barone） 和在 ABC 情景喜剧《中间》（2009-2018 年）中饰演弗朗西斯“弗兰基”赫克而闻名。\n\n希顿曾三次获得艾美奖——两次获得黄金时段艾美奖喜剧系列杰出女主角奖 人人都爱雷蒙德，以及作为帕特里夏希顿派对主持人的日间艾美奖杰出烹饪节目奖（2015-2016 年）。","name":"帕特里夏·希顿","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"帕特里夏·海倫·希頓（Patricia Helen Heaton，1958 年 3 月 4 日-），美國女演員。她因在 CBS 情景喜劇《人人都愛雷蒙德》（1996 - 2005 年）中飾演黛布拉·巴隆 （Debra Barone） 和在 ABC 情景喜劇《中間》（2009 - 2018 年）中飾演弗朗西斯“弗蘭基”赫克而聞名。\n\n希頓曾三次獲得艾美獎——兩次獲得黃金時段艾美獎喜劇系列傑出女主角獎 人人都愛雷蒙德，以及作為帕特里夏希頓派對主持人的日間艾美獎傑出烹飪節目獎（2015 - 2016 年）。","name":"帕特里夏·希頓","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Патриція Гітон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"퍼트리샤 히턴","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Патриция Хитон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"פטרישיה היטון","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"パトリシア・ヒートン","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RS","iso_639_1":"sr","name":"Srpski","english_name":"Serbian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Патриша Хитон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MK","iso_639_1":"mk","name":"","english_name":"Macedonian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Патриша Хитон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"پاتریشیا هیتون","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"LV","iso_639_1":"lv","name":"Latviešu","english_name":"Latvian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Patrīcija Hītone","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BG","iso_639_1":"bg","name":"български език","english_name":"Bulgarian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Патриша Хийтън","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HY","iso_639_1":"hy","name":"","english_name":"Armenian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Պատրիսիա Հիթոն","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"باتريشيا هيتون","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Πατρίσια Χίτον","primary":false}}]}},"tv_84737_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1773689205982,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/jzeavatG8IStoIOk0UfP