. Darin übernahm sie den Part der Priya. Einen größeren Bekanntheitsgrad erlangte die talentierte Mimin ab 2014. In dem \"Vampire Diaries\"-Spin-Off \"The Originals\" ist Nishi in der wiederkehrenden Rolle der Gia zu sehen.\n\nDoch nicht nur als Schauspielerin ist sie aktiv, sondern auch im Bereich Musik. Sie ist bisher die jüngste Musikerin die bis dato mehr als 500 Gesangs- und Tanzaufführungen in zwölf Ländern hatte.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HU","iso_639_1":"hu","name":"Magyar","english_name":"Hungarian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ниши Мунши","primary":false}}]}},"person_1234455_translations":{"at":1773689209894,"data":{"id":1234455,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hitomi Kurihara","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"栗原瞳，是一名日本演员，出生于日本茨城县，代表作品《稻川淳二的战悚怪谈》《东京塔》等。曾与石之森章太郎Shôtarô Ishinomori合作过。","name":"栗原瞳","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"栗原瞳","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"쿠리하라 히토미","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hitomi Kurihara","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"栗原瞳，是一名日本演員，出生於日本茨城縣，代表作品《稻川淳二的戰悚怪談》《東京鐵塔：我的母親父親》等。曾與石之森章太郎 Shôtarô Ishinomori 合作過。","name":"栗原瞳","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Хітомі Куріхара","primary":false}}]}},"person_1563799_translations":{"at":1773689210214,"data":{"id":1563799,"t